title: Problem with victorious maokai skin.
body: So i logged in and got my icon and maokai as a champion but the victorious skin shows as unavailable but my friends got it. Do i have to wait longer and i will receive the skin or is it just a bug?

replies.body: yeah, got the same problem here. I got the champ but i didn't get the skin. Rito pls?
Yeah, rewards are nearly all done but not entirely.  Some players are still missing their victorious skins, but don't worry!  They are coming, just hang tight!
